</span>
<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">Yep. its finally about 75% there. <br/>It has the greatest relic hunters, the Templars, the most secret unknown sects like the Black Darkhads and of course<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">Yep. its finally about 75% there. <br />It has the greatest relic hunters, the Templars, the most secret unknown sects like the Black Darkhads and of course the most unique and amazing locations yet again. <br />Facts, prophecies and of course a shut down of the world which was predicted.<br />Thinking October release as it all depends on the how long the edit process takes. <a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
</span>
</div>
</div>
<div class='communityAnswerFooter'>

