        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1744948762" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer14690291131657096584">A great read.<br/>I didn&apos;t know what to expect when I started this book but it soon pulled me in.<br/>This book had everything History,suspense,horror and supernatural tones.<br/>It reminded me of The Da Vinci Code its a well researched book.<br/>Read it well worth it.<br/><br/>Thank you to the Author Netgalley and Publisher for a chance to read this book.</span>
  <span id="freeText14690291131657096584" style="display:none">A great read.<br />I didn't know what to expect when I started this book but it soon pulled me in.<br />This book had everything History,suspense,horror and supernatural tones.<br />It reminded me of The Da Vinci Code its a well researched book.<br />Read it well worth it.<br /><br />Thank you to the Author Netgalley and Publisher for a chance to read this book.</span>
