      <div class=" clearFloats bigBox"><div class="h2Container gradientHeaderContainer"><h2 class="brownBackground"><a href="/work/quotes/49462586-the-devil-s-prayer">Quotes from The Devil&#39;s Prayer</a></h2></div><div class="bigBoxBody"><div class="bigBoxContent containerWithHeaderContent">
          <div class="stacked" tyle="padding-bottom:15px">
            <span class="readable">&ldquo;The clear night, so distant from any light pollution, had summoned every star in the sky to shine.&rdquo;</span>
